aplus_text: STRAUSS helps you develop a holistic approach towards a healthy, balanced mind and body.At STRAUSS we believe fitness is a passion and confidence builder. Expressing passion through fitness is a great way to feel alive and engaged in the world - truly the good and simple pleasure.Built to last, our solid core, EVA foam roller is made from top grade materials, and won’t lose its shape over time, even with daily use. Its lightweight materials make transport a breeze, and its compact design allows you to properly focus pressure on the affected areas.Its compact size allows you to target specific muscle groups and pain points. Increase blood flow and circulation to your muscles and soft tissue before and after workouts. Enjoy benefits like decreased recovery time from injuries and increased mobility.  Beginners and athletes alike see the same relief from sore muscles, sciatica, plantar fasciitis, back pain, shin splints and reduction in scar tissue. This is a very advanced foam roller, but it’s one that even beginners can use effectively!Rollers made from EVA foam deliver unmatched durability. These “professional strength” foam rollers are built to withstand the type of heavy, repeated use often found in gyms, clinics or Pilates studiosDeep tissue massage works by triggering the body’s natural healing responses, causing a series of physiological reactions that lead to pain relief and relaxation in the belly of the muscle.They are easy to use on any flat surface at home, park, office or anywhere you may need muscle pain relief.

The main handle on the jump rope vibrates to remind the countdown time is ended, and SkipJoy will record the circles you jump and calories you burn and other data.- You can set the quantity: 50, 100, 500, 1000, etc., and you can also customize the quantity. The main handle on the jump rope vibrates to remind the counting is ended, and SkipJoy will record the time you cost and calories you burn and other data. bullets:

It'll link to your smartphone via Bluetooth and the free SkipJoy app (available from App Store and Google Play) to let you measure the number of jumps, calories burned, time elapsed and your overall fitness progress.  
, 【WORKOUT ROPE - THREE FITNESS MODES】"Free Skip", "Countdown Timer" & "Countdown Number", three skipping modes for you to choose, stay motivated, and work out smarter. Perfect weight loss equipment and workout equipment for women and men. Ideal fitness jump rope for exercises, fitness, workout, boxing, gym, cardio, or just for daily exercise.  
, DATA RECORD & SHARING】The smart rope can record your daily exercise and graph it, you can check the daily / weekly/ monthly / yearly graph to see if you achieved your goal. At the end of your workout you can create some nice data images to share on social media, which makes you to push yourself and achieve ever loftier fitness goals.  
, 【CONVENIENT and DURABILITY】Steel rope protected by PVC sheathing makes it a more durable skipping rope. That also makes it suitable for the floor of any material like tarmac, pavement, patio, etc.  
, 【ADJUSTABLE JUMP ROPE】The jumping rope for exercise is 300cm/9.6 feet long and can be adjusted quickly according to your height. Suitable for adults and children. Built-in high quality ball bearings to avoids the twisting, winding or bending, This jump rope ensure fast and stable rotation.

, Comes with a carry case- We have included a high-quality carrying bag along with the massage roller for convenient storage and handling. The strap is adjustable to accommodate diverse body types.

aplus_text: Strauss helps you develop a holistic approach towards a healthy, balanced mind and body.At Strauss we believe fitness is a passion and confidence builder. Expressing passion through fitness is a great way to feel alive and engaged in the world - truly the best simple pleasure.Kettlebells are a great choice for those who want to tone their muscles, develop core and functional strength and strengthen their joints. They work a complete range of muscles when you swing them backwards and forwards or from side to side. These vinyl coated Kettlebells have a strong molded construction with an ergonomically designed handle for enhanced comfort. They incorporate an anti-slip base, ensuring extra safety and are supplied with a fully detailed workout chart.The built-to-last Kettlebell features high-quality solid PVC Plastic construction. Its durable design ensures safe, reliable performance from one workout to the next, so you can keep the focus on your in-the-zone routine.Kettlebell training is well recognized for its profound effects in developing cardiovascular endurance whilst also developing muscular strength using complex compound, ideal for improving core strength and stability. These benefits make Kettlebells ideally suited to activities such as Crossfit and circuit training. Kettlebells are exercise routines are high in intensity, developing speed, strength and cardiovascular endurance, providing maximum weight loss results with short blasts.Keep your fitness routine interesting and effective with help Kettlebell. With its round ball-like profile and integrated loop handle, the Kettlebell works as weight resistance and as a counterbalance for a variety of upper- and lower-body exercises. Use the Kettlebell to exercise all major muscle groups, including arms, chest, back, ABS, and legs. The benefits of Kettlebell exercises range from building muscles, enhancing core strength, and improving balance to promoting better bone health, burning calories, boosting energy levels, enhancing mood, and more.  The large handles on the Solid PVC Plastic Kettlebells are designed to improve grip, stability and control throughout a range of moves and exercises. The Kettlebells are built with the weight off-center, which activates and engages stabilizing muscles to develop more controlled muscle movement.Kettlebells make ballistic and swinging movements easier, and allow for swing and release moves with added safety and added grip, wrist, arm and core strengthening. Typical Kettlebell exercises build strength and endurance, particularly in the lower back, legs, and shoulders, and increase grip strength. , FLAT BOTTOM FOR STABILITY: Enable upright storage, ideal for renegade rows, handstands, mounted pistol squats & other exercises requiring a kettlebell with a flat bottom  
, GREAT FOR ALL GYM GOERS: Strauss Kettlebells is available in 4 Kg weights, allowing you to work out many muscle groups and body parts with performing swings, deadlifts or get-ups.
